name: High Vacuum
description:
“High Vacuum is to be understood as a per subtractionem and technically produced condition. The organizational power of the well-organized void becomes visible in scientific insights and artistic practices, in material aggregates and socio-technical constellations around its production and use.”
– Rachele Delucchi 

Rachele Delucchi is a historian of science and technology and a research associate at the Chair for History of Technology at ETH Zurich (Switzerland).
